{
  "folder": "amvZpMtjfmV6n2Cm",
  "name": "Jutsu Absorption",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "Ofn6u22OWnuhEnWX",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Otsutsuki.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You extend your hand in an attempt to absorb an oncoming attack. If the triggering Jutsu is of C-Rank or lower, you automatically absorb the Jutsu into your palm, nullifying the effects and saving it for later.</p><p data-start=\"212\" data-end=\"584\">If the Jutsu is of B-Rank or higher, you and the caster make contested Ninshou checks. If you win the check, the Jutsu is absorbed. If you lose the check, you gain vulnerability to the triggering damage of the Jutsu. A Jutsu that has been absorbed remains in your body for as long as you continue to concentrate on it, paying the concentration cost of the absorbed Jutsu.</p><p data-start=\"586\" data-end=\"780\">As an action, you can release the absorbed Jutsu as if you had cast it, ignoring any keyword requirements. If you lose concentration on this Jutsu, the absorbed Jutsu fizzles away and is wasted.</p><p data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"939\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node><strong data-start=\"782\" data-end=\"802\">At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this Jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost by 3 and increase the Jutsu that are automatically absorbed by 1 Rank.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
    "source": {
      "custom": ""
    },
    "activation": {
      "type": "reaction",
      "cost": 1,
      "condition": "(which you take when targeted by an attack roll, or forced to make a saving throw from a Ninjutsu.)"
